---
title: Thai-Style Beef & Pear Slaw with Ginger Dressing & Crushed Peanuts
description: This dish is a mad genius, with flavour explosions going off in every bite. The beef strips are served on top of a fragrant and creamy slaw with notes of both ginger and garlic. We say that sounds (and tastes) like success!

